<ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left:15px;">
<li>
    <span class="label label-danger" style="color:black;">Note:</span> This section may be obsolete now, as zerocoin code was removed from the client as of recent releases.
</li>
<li>
    A more recent build error is related to a non existent Zerocoin folder in /obj . Create the directory:
</li>
    <li>
<pre style="max-width:750px;">
