    <li>If running into a DB 4.8 error you need to change <code>#include &lt;db_cxx.h&gt;</code> to <code>#include &lt;db4.8/db_cxx.h&gt;</code> on line 14 in <code>Gridcoin-Research/src/db.h</code></li>
    <li>
        There is an issue with the permission of .Gridcoinresearch. Simply change the ownership of the file from root to user: <code>chown $USER -R ~/.GridcoinResearch</code>
    </li>
</ul>
